column4: sorry i missed what you said to my last question i was stuck in fullscreen
refresh my memory as to the question
i was asking question about parallel0 nor being found
yeah.. that means you don't have a parallel port on your actual computer
if you don't have a parallel port on your actual computer.... your virtual machine can't have one
won't crash the vm or anything
you might get a similar message regarding serial ports if your actual machine doesn't have any of those either
most vms you get off the net (including those made by easyvmx) have support for serial/parellel ports on the off chance that your machine has them
cool ill just set it not to look for them
